409
00:38:17,940 --> 00:38:20,400
for lying to you after all these years.

410
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:23,000
Dad.

411
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:25,780
I'm sorry.

412
00:38:26,740 --> 00:38:30,600
You took on the role of a father and a mother

413
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:33,380
for all these years.

414
00:38:33,380 --> 00:38:35,560
Yet, I still blamed you.

415
00:38:35,560 --> 00:38:37,640
I'm sorry!

416
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:46,780
Chi-chi, you've grown up.

417
00:38:51,540 --> 00:38:52,660
Oh right!

418
00:38:52,660 --> 00:38:57,220
Chi-chi, did you come back with Xu Fang?

419
00:38:57,220 --> 00:39:00,120
I heard that he is going abroad?

